## FULL SIDECAR API CONTRACT

All responses: `Content-Type: application/json`
Format: `{ success: boolean, data: any, error?: string }`

### Core (unchanged)
- POST /index вЂ” start indexing
- GET /index/status/:jobId вЂ” indexing progress
- GET /health вЂ” model + index status
- POST /agent/ask вЂ” single-turn agent call
- POST /agent/plan вЂ” multi-step task planner
- POST /agent/plan/:planId/execute вЂ” execute next step
- GET /shards/preview вЂ” preview context without calling LLM

### NEW: Multi-Agent Review
```
POST /review/start
Request:  { activeFile, cursorLine, projectPath, selection? }
Response: { reviewId, agents: ['architect','security','performance','test'] }

GET /review/:reviewId/stream  (SSE)
Streams: { agentType, status: 'running'|'done', result?: ReviewResult }

ReviewResult: {
  agentType: string,
  severity: 'info'|'warning'|'error',
  findings: [{ line, message, suggestion }],
  diff?: string
}
```

### NEW: Project Memory
```
POST /memory/record
Request:  { taskDescription, filesEdited, diffAccepted, latencyMs }
Response: { memoryId }

GET /memory/query
Request:  { task, projectPath, topK: 5 }
Response: { memories: [{ id, taskDescription, weight, filesEdited, timestamp }] }

GET /memory/top
Request:  { projectPath, limit: 20 }
Response: { memories: [...] }

DELETE /memory/:memoryId
Response: { deleted: true }
```

### NEW: Causal Debug
```
POST /debug/cause
Request:  { stackTrace, errorMessage, projectPath }
Response: {
  rootCauseFile, rootCauseLine, explanation,
  fix: { diff, targetFile },
  causalChain: [{ frame, file, line, contribution }]
}
```

### NEW: Semantic Drift
```
GET /drift/status
Request:  { projectPath }
Response: { driftedFunctions: [{ file, name, oldSemantic, newSemantic, distance }] }

POST /drift/acknowledge/:functionId
Response: { acknowledged: true }
```

### NEW: Edit Genome
```
POST /genome/consent  { accepted: boolean }
GET  /genome/status   в†’ { enabled, recordCount, lastSync }
GET  /genome/stats    в†’ { totalEdits, acceptRate, topFiles, avgLatency }
POST /genome/export   в†’ triggers local export to .neurocode/genome/export-{date}.jsonl
```

### NEW: LLM Models
```
GET /llm/models
Response: { models: [{ id, owned_by? }] }

POST /llm/resolve
Request:  { modelSelection, selectedModel, intent, chatMode }
Response: { modelId, reason }
```

### NEW: Cross-Repo
```
POST /crossrepo/register  { projectPath, projectId, projectName }
GET  /crossrepo/list      в†’ { projects: [{id, name, fileCount, lastIndexed}] }
POST /crossrepo/search    { query, topK, excludeProjectId? }
в†’ { results: [{file, project, reason, tokenCount}] }
```

